The experimental values obtained from the relative responsivity tests were subjected to uncertainties caused by the cryostat window transmittance (χw\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
